title: Zoe Walker
text:
My name is Zoe Walker and I am currently a Biological Sciences graduate student at California State Polytechnic University, Pomona in Dr. Juanita Jellyman’s lab. My thesis project is about understanding the impact of THC on the placenta in a mouse model. I am interested in pursuing a career in the biological data science field.


M.S. in Biological Science, 2023 - Present

B.S. in Biotechnology minor in Chemistry, 2022
